         <div class="hidden-block">
 <p>Dear Ladies and Gentlemen,<br /><br />We are lucky to be able to work in a wonderful building with rich traditions. Its history is inseparably connected with the economic development of the Russian state and owes much to the participation of foreign merchants. We have not only preserved its impressive heritage but also outfitted the building with the latest technology. Thus, the concept of the future office centre was born: Heritage with a modern touch. <br />The building has once again become a place where the representative offices of foreign companies with excellent reputations and their own traditions are located. Comfort, mutual respect, honesty, and&nbsp; constant striving to meet the individual needs of each tenant company create a unique business environment. <br />If you check out the "History" page, you will definitely learn something new about New St. Isaac's.<br />Moreover, if you find suitable premises listed on the "Offices available for rent" page we will be glad to have you as a tenant!</p>
<div class="director">
          <img src="/images/director.gif" alt="Директор" />
           Irina Rudukhina
